        "Alerting uses a custom anomaly detection model trained on 6 months of historical data, achieving 97.2% precision at 89.1% recall.",
        "The system requires a minimum of 3 nodes with 64GB RAM each for production deployment.",
        "All data is encrypted at rest using AES-256-GCM with keys rotated every 24 hours."
    ]
}
